title: Gold ranked 5's
body:
Looking for all roles except support for a semi serious ranked team. Not looking to move though the ranks super fast just looking for some good fun!
Leave your IGN, Role, top champs, and if you have skype or curse!
Hopefully we can get a good team going!!
